n implementing vector meson dominance. The role of\nchiral anomalies in the EM lagrangian is briefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2005 00:04:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2005 18:16:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
